Class PodcastPerson

java.lang.Object
com.apptasticsoftware.rssreader.module.podcast.PodcastPerson
public class PodcastPerson extends Object
Represents a person of interest to a podcast, primarily intended to identify people like hosts, co-hosts, and guests. This class is flexible enough to allow fuller credits using roles and groups as defined in the Podcast Taxonomy Project.
